node.text:
“I was humbled to see the wealth of ideas from fellow young leaders in the areas of #health and #education. It was inspiring to see the energy and innovation.”

In March, Obinna was one of the 57 amazing participants in our Nigeria Hack – and he shared the above thoughts on his experience innovating and collaborating for the #GlobalGoals.
Having worked in the health sector for many years, Obinna has great insights on how Nigeria as a country can ensure all citizens have #GoodHealthAndWellbeing.

Listen to this voice note to learn more about why Obinna is taking part in the #YOUTHPOWERHACKS.

#Goal3

@restlessdevelopment @theglobalgoals
Well done, Obinna! Very proud to see you take a leading role! 👏
